WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.690 --> 00:00:01.830
<v Instructor>Look over your shoulder</v>

2
00:00:01.830 --> 00:00:03.303
to see what's behind you.

3
00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:07.473
Move into primary position for the appropriate lane.

4
00:00:09.150 --> 00:00:12.420
Control your speed and choose the most appropriate gear

5
00:00:12.420 --> 00:00:13.983
as you approach the junction.

6
00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:16.530
Signal if appropriate

7
00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:19.030
in the direction you wish to leave the roundabout.

8
00:00:20.970 --> 00:00:24.150
Give way to road users coming from your right.

9
00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:27.933
If necessary and appropriate, signal your intentions.

10
00:00:30.090 --> 00:00:32.100
Move left when there is enough space

11
00:00:32.100 --> 00:00:34.260
as you approach your exit.

12
00:00:34.260 --> 00:00:36.630
Look around before you exit the roundabout,

13
00:00:36.630 --> 00:00:38.643
checking for anyone undertaking.

